---
import problemImg from '@/assets/images/9c00e61600b0.jpg';
---

<section class="section s3-problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="s3-problem__layout">

      <div class="s3-problem__content">

        <h2 class="s3-problem__heading">Why Most Anti-Aging Treatments Fail</h2>

        <h4 class="s3-problem__subheading">
          Discover why traditional skincare leaves Millburn and Short Hills residents searching for real solutions
        </h4>

        <p class="eyebrow s3-problem__label">The Hidden Truth About Aging Skin</p>

        <div class="s3-problem__problems">

          <div class="s3-problem__item">
            <div class="s3-problem__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F9F4;</div>
            <div class="s3-problem__item-body">
              <h3 class="s3-problem__item-title">Creams Miss the Mark</h3>
              <p class="s3-problem__item-desc">
                Traditional skincare products can't reach the underlying muscle contractions that cause expression lines. No matter how expensive, topical creams work only on the surface, leaving the real cause of wrinkles completely unaddressed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="s3-problem__item">
            <div class="s3-problem__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F3E0;</div>
            <div class="s3-problem__item-body">
              <h3 class="s3-problem__item-title">At-Home Treatments Fall Short</h3>
              <p class="s3-problem__item-desc">
                Facial exercises and DIY remedies rarely deliver significant results. Without addressing the muscular activity that creates lines over time, these approaches cannot produce the smooth, refreshed appearance that patients want.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="s3-problem__item">
            <div class="s3-problem__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F48A;</div>
            <div class="s3-problem__item-body">
              <h3 class="s3-problem__item-title">Over-the-Counter Promises</h3>
              <p class="s3-problem__item-desc">
                Anti-aging products offer temporary improvements but fail to address the root cause of dynamic wrinkles. The result is a cycle of purchasing products that deliver short-term hydration but no lasting change.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <p class="eyebrow s3-problem__label">The Real Problem</p>

        <p class="s3-problem__body">
          Dynamic wrinkles form when facial muscles repeatedly contract during expressions like smiling, squinting, and frowning. Over time, these repeated movements create permanent creases in the overlying skin. This is a muscular issue, not a topical one.
        </p>

        <p class="s3-problem__body">
          As we age, our skin also loses collagen and elastin, making it less able to bounce back after muscle movements. The combination of weakened skin structure and constant muscular activity accelerates the formation of lines and wrinkles that cannot be reversed by surface-level treatments.
        </p>

        <p class="s3-problem__body">
          Understanding the true cause of aging skin makes it clear why so many anti-aging solutions fail to deliver lasting results.
        </p>

        <p class="eyebrow s3-problem__label">The Better Way Forward</p>

        <p class="s3-problem__body">
          Botox at Menon Medispa directly addresses the muscular cause of expression lines. By temporarily relaxing the specific muscles responsible for wrinkle formation, Botox allows the overlying skin to smooth and recover, delivering visible results that no topical product can match.
        </p>

        <p class="s3-problem__body">
          Under the care of Dr. Menon, your Botox treatment is precisely calibrated to preserve your natural expressions while softening the lines that age you. The result is a refreshed, rested appearance that looks completely natural.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="s3-problem__img-col">
        <img
          src={problemImg.src}
          alt="Anti-aging skin concerns addressed at Menon Medispa Millburn NJ"
          class="s3-problem__img"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="488"
          height="428"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-problem__layout {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .s3-problem__content {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s3-problem__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-problem__subheading {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .s3-problem__label {
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .s3-problem__problems {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-block: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .s3-problem__item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .s3-problem__icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .s3-problem__item-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .s3-problem__item-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-problem__item-desc, .s3-problem__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-problem__img-col {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 380px;
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s3-problem__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .s3-problem__img-col {
      width: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s3-problem__layout {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .s3-problem__img-col {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
